\f1\b 1. FutureYou Cinematic Reveal \'97 Build This First
\f0\b0 \
                                                                                \
  At onboarding completion, after the user has defined their studio:\
  - User optionally uploads a photo (headshot, workspace, mood board) \uc0\u8594          \
  \cf3 set_image\cf2                                                                      \
  - Backend constructs a richly detailed prompt from their formation data:\
  creator type + stage + studio name + tier                                     \
  - \cf3 schedule_prompt\cf2  at chunks 0, 5, 10 queues a 3-act cinematic sequence of     \
  their future                                                             \
  - Their actual image animates into a living vision of where they're headed    \
                                                                            \
  The \cf3 set_seed\cf2  tied to their \cf3 email\cf2  hash means their FutureYou world is          \
  
\f1\b consistent and personal
\f0\b0  \'97 every time they return, it's the same world,        \
  evolving only when they hit new stages.                                       \
                                                                                \
  
